{"tid":1682566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟日報迫害義士無人理，係咪當義士condom？","createTime":"2019-10-30T06:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:55:24.000Z","uid":2429,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7ef169ae6509dec99b3459936d8eb81425d448","tid":1682566,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191030/20796517?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796517%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt32Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=261a15f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796517%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=fee82c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191030/20796517?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n記者開罪警察《經濟》疑秋後算賬炒3人<br />\n2019-10-30<br />\n頭條<br />\n<br />\n警方記者會前日重開後，多名記者要求直接進入問答環節。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《經濟日報》記者前日在警方記者會重開後，要求直接進入問答環節，遭主持記者會的警察公共關係科警司高振邦斥喝並要脅驅逐出場。該記者即日便被《經濟日報》主管以不滿表現為由發出警告，另有一名參與反送中報道的記者更被辭退，有員工相信涉及新聞審查。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「港已無民主」美參院加快出招<br />\n<br />\n促警答問題　遭主管警告<br />\n<br />\n《經濟日報》前副社長石鏡泉曾於建制撐警會發表「藤條水喉通打仔」言論，公然鼓吹暴力。前日警方記者會因有記者抗議警暴而暫停，多名記者在復會後要求直接進入問答環節，主持高振邦充耳不聞，連番叫多位記者收聲。無綫電視記者被要求收聲後，《經濟日報》記者指出「記者會係畀記者講嘢㗎嘛」，要求直接問答，高僅稱「麻煩你收聲啦」、「你咁樣打斷阿Sir嘅講嘢」，記者回應「咁你畀我哋問，你答咪可以囉」，高則恐嚇「如果你再係咁，我請你出去㗎喇」。《明報》記者加入發問，《經濟日報》記者再要求警方澄清會否聆聽記者聲音，惟高振邦只關心上司能否發言，「你可唔可以畀阿Sir講咗先啊？」<br />\n<br />\n《經濟日報》即日以不滿表現為由向該記者發出警告。據悉，《經濟日報》另一名曾在警方四點鐘例會提出尖銳問題的記者，以及兩名攝影記者亦於同日被公司以「資源重組」為由辭退。該記者接受查詢時稱難證實是審查，但有《經濟日報》員工則相信裁員決定涉及新聞審查。《經濟日報》昨相關報道主稿以拘捕數字為題，抗議內容在尾段僅百多字，大部份篇幅是警方批評記者的內容，關於記者訴求僅有「指摘警方於示威現場暴力對待記者，阻礙採訪」。<br />\n<br />\n記協前日聲明呼籲傳媒機構切勿對參與抗議的記者秋後算賬，記協主席楊健興昨補充指，難以評論不同傳媒對記者的要求，希望傳媒主管體諒前線採訪時面對的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾偉龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無人理就以後全部義士都畀人炒晒，無人再敢出聲，革命正式收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b261933d82c3406a1994d68acfca9cc952cb540f","tid":1682566,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"842eb970c66abbb07d420cce072d6679962fb442","tid":1682566,"uid":210499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:35:22.000Z","msg":"推到手足同經濟日報裝修 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440b01de89c5d626855f4a296bf45cdef652efe0","tid":1682566,"uid":210499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616e1e4c56039bc062cc3d931f3441ba3c4bae5d","tid":1682566,"uid":113187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/muwvFtj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmuwvFtj.jpg&h=f0c72dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6TNHGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6TNHGF.jpg&h=fcbe7cc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b63ae9211d99c0cb4b3fba2e53ebd02ffaae7682","tid":1682566,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"國泰迫害義士都係無人理"},{"